2 CONC e.  Their daughter, Eva Myrtilla Allison Harriger, is also buried in the corner 
2 CONC of this cemetery, under the trees on a little family plot platform.  <br><br><br
2 CONC ><br>Roy Clark and Daisy Mabel Mong Allison were the fifth generation of ancesto
2 CONC rs in America.  Roy lived from 1892 to 1978 and Daisy lived from 1898 to 1973.  
2 CONC Roy and Daisy had four children – Patricia, Robert, Yvonne and Lee.<br>They are 
2 CONC buried in Salem Cemetery, near Frogtown, PA in Clarion County.  Siblings of Roy 
