2 CONC seven children – John, Andrew, Tate, Robert James Thomas, Jane.<br>Bethel Cemete
2 CONC ry is the oldest in Indiana County and among the oldest in Western Pennsylvania.
2 CONC  223 graves sites have markers, but there are many unmarked graves. In 1935 a fi
