2 CONC s (Andrew) 13,Jacob 11, Caroline 9, Matthias 6, and Magdalene 3. The Ditz`s firs
2 CONC t winter was spent with the Eisenman family. In the spring John bought100 acres 
2 CONC and built their homestead in Fryburg.
