1 NOTE By trade, Jacob Egg was a gun maker and locksmith.  Jacob Egg wasinAmerica befo 
2 CONC re 3 Jun 1746, the date of a warrant of survey forlandissued in his name.<br><b 
2 CONC r>Jacob owned two tracts of land totaling125 acres in Upper Salford (nowSalford 
2 CONC ) Township in Philadelphia (nowMontgomery) County, Pennsylvania.<br><br>A Roman 
2 CONC Catholic, Jacob Egg mayhave chosen the homestead site for theexpress purpose o f
