1 NOTE Came to the United States at age 18 to avoid military duty He was married to Jos
2 CONC ephine After she died he married Anna Fried, a Bohemian girl.  After Anna died h
2 CONC e moved to Centralia Washington. After a few years he took the family back to Ai
2 CONC tken, Minn. where Frank Hense his oldest son of his  first wife Josephine lived.
2 CONC  Dora, Lena, Bertha, and Theodore remained in Centralia, Washington.
