1 NOTE Martin A. Nairn, 81, Shaffer Avenue, DuBois, died Tuesday, Dec. 2, 2014, at Chri
2 CONC st the King Manor.<br>Born Oct. 27, 1933, in Wishaw, he was the son of the late 
2 CONC Martin W. and Nellie Millward Nairn.<br>He was married to Frances "Chickie" Torr
2 CONC ell Nairn. She survives.<br>He retired from Intel as an engineer and production 
2 CONC manager after many years of service.<br>He was a graduate of Pennsylvania State 
2 CONC University where he was a member of the Alumni Association. He was also a member
2 CONC  of the Knights of Columbus.<br>He loved to golf and go camping. He also enjoyed
2 CONC  cooking and watching all sports, and was well known in his youth for his wonder
2 CONC ful voice, singing at many local events.<br>Divorced from Magarey Reinsel IN 197
2 CONC 1<br><br><br>Martin is survived by his children: Martin A. "Buddy" Nairn Jr. and
2 CONC  his wife, Wanda, of Phoenix, Ariz., Josef E. Nairn and his wife, Shannon, of Sa
2 CONC cramento, Calif., Jerome P. Nairn and his wife, Sue, of Long Beach, Calif., Jona
2 CONC than P. Nairn of Phoenix, Ariz., and Christopher A. Nairn of Madison, Wis.; thre
2 CONC e stepchildren: Glenda Stewart of Frederick, Md., Glenn Stewart and his wife, De
2 CONC borah, of Ft. Myers, Fla., and Gregg Stewart and his wife, Cindy, of Leesburg, V
2 CONC a.; 11 grandchildren, two great-grandchildren; a brother, Edward Nairn; and a si
2 CONC ster, Monnette Sturgill, both of Kentucky. He is also survived by his sister-in-
2 CONC law, Donna Skehan and her husband, Michael, of DuBois.<br>He was preceded in dea
2 CONC th by two brothers, Tony and Tom Nairn.<br>Visitation will be held from 2-5 p.m.
2 CONC  today (Thursday, Dec. 4, 2014) at the Goble-Baronick Funeral Home, DuBois.<br>A
2 CONC  funeral service will be held at 5 p.m. today at the funeral home with the Rev. 
2 CONC Msgr. Richard Siefer officiating.<br>Memorial donations may be made to Christ th
2 CONC e King Manor, 1100 West Long Ave., DuBois, PA 15801.<br>Online condolences may b
2 CONC e made at www.gbfuneralhome.com.
