1 NOTE The children of Henry Sr. and Elizabeth include a daughter, Rachel,whowas born i
2 CONC n 1789, according to the Burgoon Genealogy and died on May15,1854. She married A
2 CONC dam Kuhn. Rachel Reinzel Kuhn died at the age of66.She was born in 1788 or 17 89
2 CONC  and died May 15, 1854.  She was the wifeofAdam (Coon) Kuhn. (See the Burgoon ge
2 CONC nealogy). The historicalevidenceshows that she was a sister of Henry, John, Dani
2 CONC el and AnthonyandGeorge.  On June 17, 1804, Rachel and Daniel Reinzel (I as sume
2 CONC  theywerebrother and sister) were sponsors of John Casuli Son of CornneliusandMa
2 CONC gdalene Casuli at St Mary`s Church in Lebanon. In 1816, Rachel andAdamCoo n were
2 CONC  sponsors of Rachel Reinsel the daughter of George andCatherineReinsel, a nd Rac
2 CONC hel`s niece. (Baptisms of Western Pennsylvania,page 74)
