2 CONC e (Lestock) Rensel in 2002;<br>and by two brothers, William Albert Rensel, Jr., 
2 CONC and James Edward Rensel. Survivors<br>include a brother, John R. Rensel and his 
2 CONC wife, Evelyn, of Erie; several nieces and<br>nephews, including Jeff Rensel, of 
2 CONC Erie; and a dear friend, Louise Melzer, of Erie.<br>Friends may call at the Brug
