2 CONC n Clarion, the Knights of Columbus, Clarion Fire and Hose Company #1 where he se
2 CONC rved as treasurer, and the International Harvester Collectorâ€™s Club.<br>Joe lo
2 CONC ved to play cards, enjoyed watched Pittsburgh sports teams, and spending time wi
