2 CONC lravy and her husband Rob of Shippenville, PA; many beloved nieces, nephews, and
2 CONC  godchildren; and his godmother, Helen Stahlman of Clarion, PA. He is predecease
2 CONC d by a sister Karen Marie Rice, in 1961.
